      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atkaż notikke taż Wahrds\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fatka taż KUNGS\nZebaot: Ta Gawetchana tazet-\ntorta/ un peekta/ un ſeptita/ un\nDeſmita Mehnes buhs taim\nNammam Juha par Preeku/\nun par Libgſminibu/ un par lab-\nveem Swehtkeem/ tapehz mihlo-\njeet to Pateefibu / un to Meeru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fatka taż KUNGS\nZebaot: Wehl Tautas nahks/\nun dauds Piłsfahtu Eedsihwo-\ntaji.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un weena Piłsfahta Ee-\ndsihwotaji ees pee ta ohtra Ee-\ndsihwotajeem/ un fazzihș: Eima\nto KUNGU peeluhgt / un to\nKUNGU Zebaot meflecht / ir es\neeschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta nahks dauds Lau-\nschu/ un warreni Pagani mek-\nlehs to KUNGU Zebaot eekſch\nJerusalemes / un peeluhgs to\nKUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fatka taż KUNGS\nZebaot: Taż notiks taanis Dee-\nnās/ ka deſmits Wihti no wiſ-\nfadahm Paganzu Wallo dahim /\nſatwers weenu ( Drehbju )\nStuhri kahda Judu Wihra/ un\nfazzihș: Mehș eeſim ar jums/\njo mehs eeſim dsirdejscht / ka\nDeewș ar jums irrait.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Chi irr ta Nasta/ ko\nKUNGS runna p\nto Semmi Adraku/\nDamaskus fawu Duſtefcha\njo taim KUNGA M irr we\nAzz pahr teem Ziltwekeem/\npahr wiſſabm Israeta Ziltim\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir pahr Ahmatu /\neekſch winnas Rohbeschabm g\npahr Tiru un Sihdonu/ jept\nta fohti guđra irrait.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Tirus irr fewi S\nrumus uhēzehlis/ un Sudr-\nfakrahjis ka Pihtschlus/ un E\ntu ka Dubtus us Eelahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redſi/ taż KUNGS\ndsihs winnu/ un fatuls win\nStiprumu Juhrd / un rvi\ntaps no Uggunni aprichts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Askalons to redsehs un\nsees/ ir Gaza/ un zeetihș le\nSahpes lihdsar Ekronu.\npehz ka taș/ uhs fo tee rauds\ntohs irr Kauna darrijs. Un\nRehnisch no Gazas ees bo\nunAskalons ne taps eedsihwo\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un eekſch Asdodas\nwohs Sweschi/un es iſdelde\nto Wilisteru Lepnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es atxemſchu wi\nAffini no winnu Muttes/\nwinnu Negantibu no wi\nSchbeem/ ta tee arridsau n\ntam Deetwam atlifs/ ir tee l\nka weens Waldneeks eekſch\nda/ un Ekrons ka tee Jebusi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es pats apmettiſch\napf\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
